{
  "doc_id": "FC-LS",
  "source_pdf": "/Users/zwy/毕设/V7/data/raw/FC-LS.pdf",
  "page": 202,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0002",
      "text": " 183",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0003",
      "text": "Each page identifies a Binding mode PRLI operation between the Originator Nx_Port and one image",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.86,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0004",
      "text": "at the Responder Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        214.33,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0005",
      "text": "7.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        109.88,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0006",
      "text": "Process Logout",
      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        94.97,
        195.35,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0007",
      "text": "The Process Logout (PRLO) ELS request shall be used to request invalidation of the operating envi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.05,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0008",
      "text": "ronment between an image at the initiating Nx_Port and an image at the recipient Nx_Port.  PRLO",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.02,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0009",
      "text": "frees resources committed by a previous PRLI function.  ULP behavior following successful execu-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        540.02,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0010",
      "text": "tion of the PRLO function is specified in the corresponding FC-4 standard. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        425.43,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0011",
      "text": "Examples of PRLO usage include image re-configuration and TYPE-specific reset of Process Login",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.0,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0012",
      "text": "Service Parameters.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        186.46,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0013",
      "text": "TYPE-specific Service Parameter settings may be reset or image pairs removed with a PRLO re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.15,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0014",
      "text": "quest and LS_ACC reply Sequence set.  Other TYPE-specific Service Parameter settings or image",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        539.88,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0015",
      "text": "pairs associated with the same or different image pairs or Nx_Ports shall be unaffected.  After TYPE-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        238.96,
        540.1,
        250.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0016",
      "text": "specific Service Parameter settings are reset or image pair is removed, Information Units may not be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.86,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0017",
      "text": "sent or received for the specified FC-4 TYPE using that image pair and Nx_Port combination speci-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        539.95,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0018",
      "text": "fied in the PRLO request.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        208.22,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0019",
      "text": "If a PRLO request is received for an image pair or FC-4 TYPE that does not exist, the request is ac-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        539.99,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0020",
      "text": "cepted, provided that no link errors are detected, and the LS_ACC response is sent.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        467.11,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0021",
      "text": "The Nx_Port originating the PRLO request shall not consider an image pair to be removed until it re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        540.04,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0022",
      "text": "ceives an LS_ACC reply Sequence.  The Nx_Port responding to the PRLO request shall not consider",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        539.99,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0023",
      "text": "an image pair to be removed or TYPE-specific Service Parameter settings to be reset, as appropri-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        539.96,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0024",
      "text": "ate, until the LS_ACC reply Sequence is sent.  An Nx_Port that receives a P_BSY, F_BSY, P_RJT,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        540.03,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0025",
      "text": "or F_RJT reply in response to a PRLO request may retry the PRLO request.  The number of retries is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        540.0,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0026",
      "text": "system dependent.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        180.45,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0027",
      "text": "Unless the requesting Nx_Port receives a valid response to a PRLO request, that Nx_Port shall not",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        540.02,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0028",
      "text": "assume that the requested action has or has not taken place. If the Nx_Port that originates a PRLO",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        540.03,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0029",
      "text": "request receives no valid response, the Nx_Port should retry the request.  The number of retries is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.91,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0030",
      "text": "vendor unique.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        162.03,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0031",
      "text": "A PRLO page identifies a particular image pair to logout by marking either or both the Originator Pro-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        540.03,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0032",
      "text": "cess Associator and the Responder Process Associator.  Only that image pair is logged out.  No fur-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.02,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0033",
      "text": "ther communication for the affected FC-4(s) is possible between these two images.  It is the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        539.93,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0034",
      "text": "responsibility of the ULPs to ensure that all active operations over an image pair have been orderly",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.92,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0035",
      "text": "and properly terminated prior to issuing a PRLO request. Following PRLO execution, all active Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        540.04,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0036",
      "text": "quences and Exchanges shall be terminated by invoking Abort Sequence (ABTS). On-going opera-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        539.92,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0037",
      "text": "tions and states for other image pairs are not affected.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        335.38,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0038",
      "text": "If a ULP attempts to communicate over an image pair that has not been established or has been ab-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        540.08,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0039",
      "text": "normally terminated, the communication shall be acknowledged in the normal manner.  The Origina-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.06,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0040",
      "text": "tor may then perform a PRLO operation for the affected image pair in order to properly terminate the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        539.96,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p202_s0041",
      "text": "operating environment at both the Originator and Responder.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        365.98,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}